data.field: Private automobile. Motorcycle or scooter. Taxi. Bus. Subway / Train. Bicycle. Skateboard / Inline skates. Walk. Ferry / Sail / Paddle. Internet / Telephone / Fax. Airplane / Helecopter. Telekinesis / Telepathy / Teleportation. A transporter. Hallucinogens. Astral projection. My Perl-based bot has fooled people for years into believing I'm currently at my desk. The unemployed never commute. I never go home.
